title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 25 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 25 2021
description:
Conservative commentator Candace Owens of The Daily Wire joined Clay and Buck to discuss the breaking stories of the day. Will Biden be able to complete his four-year term? Republicans need to do their due diligence on candidates. Pelosi pushes for vaccinations for children. If Trump can be impeached for a phone call, how can Biden not be impeached on the Afghanistan disaster? Herschel Walker running for Senate in Georgia.
